### Create Campaign
POST http://localhost:5000/api/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer <campaigner_access_token>

title=Help Injured Dog
description=Need urgent surgery support for rescued dog
goalAmount=50000
category=Medical
location=Hyderabad
urgencyLevel=critical
coverImage=@./fixtures/dog.jpg


